message.text:
𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐇𝐮𝐧𝐭 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓: 𝐆𝐢𝐧𝐭𝐨 𝐚𝐭 𝐆𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐈𝐲𝐨𝐧𝐠 𝐓𝐮𝐤𝐥𝐚𝐬𝐢𝐧! 📸🌟

Our #LakbayPiyu2025 comes to an end. Thank you Tamaraws for shining with us. ✨ 

We hope that you all felt our highest energies and join OJFINEX for more fun and learnings! We're waiting for all of you, FINANCE TAMS! 🫵🏻🔰

𝐎𝐮𝐫 𝐌𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐩𝐨𝐫𝐭𝐬 𝐀𝐩𝐩𝐥𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐚𝐫𝐞 𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐥𝐥 𝐨𝐩𝐞𝐧 𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐥 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟎. For the last time, CEBUkan niyo na sa OJFINEX! ⭐️

#FEUOJFINEX
#FEUIABF
#TATAKFINANCE
#CreateTheFEUtureWithOJFINEX 
#CEBUkanMoSaOJFINEX

message.text:
𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐇𝐮𝐧𝐭 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓: 𝐆𝐢𝐧𝐭𝐨 𝐚𝐭 𝐆𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐈𝐲𝐨𝐧𝐠 𝐓𝐮𝐤𝐥𝐚𝐬𝐢𝐧! 📸🌟

Our #LakbayPiyu2025 comes to an end. Thank you Tamaraws for shining with us. ✨ 

We hope that you all felt our highest energies and join OJFINEX for more fun and learnings! We're waiting for all of you, FINANCE TAMS! 🫵🏻🔰

𝐎𝐮𝐫 𝐌𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐩𝐨𝐫𝐭𝐬 𝐀𝐩𝐩𝐥𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐚𝐫𝐞 𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐥𝐥 𝐨𝐩𝐞𝐧 𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐥 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟎. For the last time, CEBUkan niyo na sa OJFINEX! ⭐️

#FEUOJFINEX
#FEUIABF
#TATAKFINANCE
#CreateTheFEUtureWithOJFINEX 
#CEBUkanMoSaOJFINEX
